14 (1) A REVOCATORY ACT ON THE DEED; OR
15 (2) A TESTAMENTARY DOCUMENT EXECUTED BY THE TRANSFEROR,
16 EVEN IF THE TESTAMENTARY DOCUMENT IS EXECUTED AFTER THE DATE OF
