15 IF YOU SELECTED OPTION TWO AND YOU ARE THE BENEFICIARY OCCUPYING THE
16 PROPERTY, PLEASE COMPLETE THE FOLLOWING:
17 I, ______________________ (PRINT NAME), DO HEREBY CERTIFY AND AFFIRM UNDER
18 THE PENALTIES OF PERJURY THAT I CURRENTLY LIVE AT AND WILL CONTINUE TO
19 LIVE AT THE ABOVE–REFERENCED PROPERTY, FOLLOWING THE RECORDING OF
20 THIS NOTIFICATION. I SHALL OCCUPY THE PROPERTY AS MY PRINCIPAL RESIDENCE
21 FOR AT LEAST 7 OF THE NEXT 12 MONTHS.
